\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
Interactive drawing canvas for creating and editing geometric shapes.

Extends {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{javafx.\+scene.\+layout.\+Pane}} to provide a mouse-\/driven canvas where the user can draw, select, move, scale, rotate, and recolor shapes. Supports three shape types\+: circles, rectangles, and polygons.

Interaction summary\+:
\begin{DoxyItemize}
\item Left-\/click + drag on empty area\+: draws a new shape (depending on active {\ttfamily \doxylink{enumToolMode}{Tool\+Mode}}).
\item Left-\/click on a shape\+: selects it (stroke thickens).
\item Left-\/click + drag on selected shape\+: moves it.
\item Scroll wheel on selected shape\+: scales it.
\item Shift + scroll on selected shape\+: rotates it.
\item Right-\/click on a shape\+: opens an inline {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{Color\+Picker}} to change fill color.
\item Double-\/click\+: finishes drawing a polygon.
\end{DoxyItemize}

