{\footnotesize\ttfamily Drawing\+Pane.\+Drawing\+Pane (\begin{DoxyParamCaption}{ }\end{DoxyParamCaption})\hspace{0.3cm}{\ttfamily [inline]}}

Constructs the \doxylink{classDrawingPane}{Drawing\+Pane} and registers all mouse event handlers.

Sets up clipping to prevent shapes from rendering outside the pane bounds, and attaches handlers for mouse press, drag, release, and scroll events. 

