\doxysubsubsection{\texorpdfstring{loadDrawing()}{loadDrawing()}}
{\footnotesize\ttfamily void Drawing\+Pane.\+load\+Drawing (\begin{DoxyParamCaption}{ }\end{DoxyParamCaption})\hspace{0.3cm}{\ttfamily [inline]}}

Loads shapes from a binary file and adds them to the current canvas.

Opens a {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{File\+Chooser}} dialog for the user to select a {\ttfamily .\+fig} file, then deserializes the shapes via {\ttfamily \doxylink{classFileIO_ad6c709a959a56be6a6ba4de18d4cf91c}{File\+IO\#load\+From\+File}} and reconstructs the corresponding Java\+FX {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{Shape}} objects with all saved properties restored. Loaded shapes are appended to the existing canvas without clearing it. \Hypertarget{classDrawingPane_a149a822032e4b00ec5baac5cffb24b2f}\label{classDrawingPane_a149a822032e4b00ec5baac5cffb24b2f} 
\index{DrawingPane@{DrawingPane}!saveDrawing@{saveDrawing}}
\index{saveDrawing@{saveDrawing}!DrawingPane@{DrawingPane}}
\doxysubsubsection{\texorpdfstring{saveDrawing()}{saveDrawing()}}
{\footnotesize\ttfamily void Drawing\+Pane.\+save\+Drawing (\begin{DoxyParamCaption}{ }\end{DoxyParamCaption})\hspace{0.3cm}{\ttfamily [inline]}}

Saves all shapes currently on the canvas to a binary file.

Converts each {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{Shape}} in the canvas into its corresponding {\ttfamily \doxylink{classShapeData}{Shape\+Data}} object (preserving all transformations and colors), then opens a {\ttfamily \doxylink{}{File\+Chooser}} dialog for the user to choose the save location. The file is saved with a {\ttfamily .\+fig} extension via {\ttfamily \doxylink{classFileIO_a63bc5a7f07d2bf9273492cd7a7d5d05f}{File\+IO\#save\+To\+File}}. \Hypertarget{classDrawingPane_a42bd6e5ca070667f1c0fbb4e73a142ac}\label{classDrawingPane_a42bd6e5ca070667f1c0fbb4e73a142ac} 
